data.title: Independent Boarding & Day School
data.meta_description: Celebration of Seniors - An independent school for boarding & day students in grades 9-12. Strong academics, marine science & sailing programs set Tabor apart from other college preparatory schools in New England.
data.text:
End-of-Year Event Photos Download or Purchase Prints

NOTE: These Tabor-provided photos are available as a courtesy to download for free or purchase as prints from SmugMug. Additional Prom and Commencement photography from third-party photographers may also be available; when such images are available, instructions for access will be emailed to families.
